     Name         : MessAngel Killer

     Aliases      : Eleni 3 Dropper

     Type/Size    : Trojan/7100 unpacked, PP-Packed 1808 byte

     Clones       : No Clones

     Symptoms     : No Symptoms

     Discovered   : 20-09-94

     Way to infect: No Infection

     Rating       : Less Dangerous

     Kickstarts   : 2.X/3.X

     Damage       : Installs the ELENI 3 virus

     Manifestation: Pretends to be a Viruskiller!

     Removal      : Delete File immediately.

     Comments     : If  you`re  starting the MessAngel trojan it gives out
                    the following text:


                    "MessAngel Killer by Docker of Twist!" ... etc.


                    After that  it openes the startup-sequence and inserts
                    at the beginning "B + [Return]".


                    Then  the  virus  writes  the manipulated startup-seq.
                    ALWAYS  with  5000 bytes no matter if the startup-seq.
                    was longer or shorter.

                    After  that  a  file  will  be written called "sys:B".
                    This  file  is 1504 byte long and is the "real" virus-
                    installer.  The  file  contains the whole ELENI3-Boot-
                    block which will be activated on the next boot up! 

                    On the screen you will get the following message:

                    MessAngel killer by Docker of Twist!
                    Checking startup-sequence...
                    VIRUS FOUND AND REMOVED!!!
                    Right to disable from memory!
                    -----------------------------
           
                    Click on this gadget to see a @{" Demo " SYSTEM V-IFF:MessAngelKiller} of the MessAngel 
                    Killer virus. Push left mouse button to return.

                    -> For Eleni 3 Virus description see "ELENI 3".

A.D / ELS 11-94
